commit_message:
Allow AZ at instance show

Reason:
 - since AZ is one of possible parameters for instance provisioning,
   it would be better to show AZ on instance show task;
Changes:
 - storring AZ as one of instance base schema colums;
 - AZ mentioned at instance model contains it;
 - tests;

